== 製作 ==
在《惡靈古堡：無盡闇黑》正式發布前，[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]][[Netflix|Netflix]]在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上意外洩露了劇集的預告片，並聲稱這將是一部「[[電腦成像|CGI]]電影」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/resident-evil-infinite-darkness-netflix-2021|title=Netflix Portugal Unexpectedly Announces RESIDENT EVIL: INFINITE DARKNESS CGI Movie|website=Gameplay Mechanix|accessdate=2020-09-28|date=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929190611/https://www.ign.com/articles/resident-evil-infinite-darkness-netflix-2021|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但不久之後便刪除了該條文<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/daily-briefs/2020-09-26/netflix-portugal-briefly-listed-resident-evil-infinite-darkness-cg-project/.164525|title=Netflix Portugal Briefly Listed Resident Evil: Infinite Darkness CG Project (Updated)|website=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|accessdate=2020-09-28|date=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930142445/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/daily-briefs/2020-09-26/netflix-portugal-briefly-listed-resident-evil-infinite-darkness-cg-project/.164525|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該系列的執行製作人[[小林裕幸|小林裕幸]]在2020年[[東京電玩展|東京電玩展]]上正式公布劇集的消息<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/resident-evil-infinite-darkness-netflix-2021|title=Resident Evil: Infinite Darkness Netflix Show Officially Announced|website=IGN|accessdate=2020-09-28|date=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929190611/https://www.ign.com/articles/resident-evil-infinite-darkness-netflix-2021|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animationmagazine.net/streaming/trailer-netflix-reveals-resident-evil-cg-anime-series-infinite-darkness/|title=Trailer: Netflix Reveals ‘Resident Evil’ CG Anime Series ‘Infinite Darkness’|website=Animation Magazine|accessdate=2020-09-28|date=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002205954/https://www.animationmagazine.net/streaming/trailer-netflix-reveals-resident-evil-cg-anime-series-infinite-darkness/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。角色由《[[惡靈古堡2|惡靈古堡2]]》的[[里昂·S·甘乃迪|里昂·S·甘乃迪]]與[[克蕾兒·雷德菲爾|克蕾兒·雷德菲爾]]擔任劇集主要角色<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/netflix-resident-evil-infinite-darkness-cg-anime-series-162642088.html|title=Netflix unveils a 'Resident Evil' CG anime series arriving in 2021|website=Engadget|accessdate=2020-09-28|date=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928015241/https://www.engadget.com/netflix-resident-evil-infinite-darkness-cg-anime-series-162642088.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年4月，在《惡靈古堡》展示活動上透露，羽住英一郎將擔任劇集的導演，而[[菅野祐悟|菅野祐悟]]擔任劇集的作曲家<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2021-04-15/resident-evil-infinite-darkness-cg-series-reveals-new-trailer-director-composer-july-debut/.171760|title=Resident Evil: Infinite Darkness CG Series Reveals New Trailer, Director, Composer, July Debut|website=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|access-date=2021-04-15|date=2021-04-15|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420030131/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2021-04-15/resident-evil-infinite-darkness-cg-series-reveals-new-trailer-director-composer-july-debut/.171760|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

